## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a44f1-106">呼び出す必要があります、<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A>永続的な作成できるようにする新しいエントリのメソッドです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a44f1-106">You must call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A> method on the new entry to make the creation permanent.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a44f1-107">このメソッドを呼び出すときに、新しいエントリの必須プロパティの値を設定できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a44f1-107">When you call this method, you can then set mandatory property values on the new entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a44f1-108">各プロバイダーの呼び出しの前に設定する必要があるプロパティの別の要件があります、<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A>メソッドが行われます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a44f1-108">The providers each have different requirements for properties that need to be set before a call to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A> method is made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a44f1-109">これらの要件が満たされず、プロバイダーで例外がスローする可能性があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a44f1-109">If those requirements are not met, the provider might throw an exception.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a44f1-110">変更をコミットする前に設定する必要がありますのあるプロパティを決定するプロバイダーに確認します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a44f1-110">Check with your provider to determine which properties must be set before committing changes.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a44f1-111">次の Visual Basic .NET 例が新たに作成<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>オブジェクトのパスを指定して、コンテナーに新しいエントリを作成し、保存されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a44f1-111">The following Visual Basic .NET example creates a new <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> object with a specified path, then creates a new entry in the container and saves it.</span></span>  

```vb  
Dim strPath As String = "IIS://localhost/W3SVC/1/Root"  
' Create a new 'DirectoryEntry' object with the given path.  
Dim myDE As New DirectoryEntry(strPath)  
Dim myEntries As DirectoryEntries = myDE.Children  
' Create a new entry 'Sample' in the container.  
Dim myDirectoryEntry As DirectoryEntry = myEntries.Add("CN=Sample", myDE.SchemaClassName)  
' Save changes of entry in the 'Active Directory Domain Services'.  
myDirectoryEntry.CommitChanges()  
Console.WriteLine(myDirectoryEntry.Name + " entry is created in container.")  
```  

